{"id":74877,"title":"Transition: driving and exercise.","abstract":"There are many social aspects to consider at the time of transition of adolescents with epilepsy. The role of both pediatric and adult health care providers includes education and guidance within the larger framework of family, society, and country. This section focuses on driving and exercise considerations for those undergoing transition. ","date":"2014-09-11","categories":"Nervous System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25209086","annotations":[{"name":"Education","weight":0.818686,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.781524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Health care","weight":0.705743,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Adolescence","weight":0.682086,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolescence"},{"name":"Pediatrics","weight":0.661902,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pediatrics"},{"name":"Physical exercise","weight":0.657269,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_exercise"},{"name":"Society","weight":0.621041,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Society"},{"name":"Social","weight":0.594254,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Social"},{"name":"Adult","weight":0.534263,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adult"},{"name":"Epilepsy","weight":0.205556,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Epilepsy"},{"name":"Health care provider","weight":0.141289,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care_provider"},{"name":"Country music","weight":0.0391252,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country_music"},{"name":"Family (biology)","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Family_(biology)"},{"name":"Driving","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Driving"},{"